This paper deals with the distributed edge coloring problem, which is a fundamental problem in distributed graph algorithms. The paper proposes a new algorithm that improves upon the previous best-known result by Kuhn [SODA '20]. The problem is related to distributed computing (cs.DC), distributed systems (cs.DS), algorithms (cs.AL), network protocols (cs.NI), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
